<exercise><statement><p>
      Find the
      
          y-intercepts
        
      for each of the following equations.
    </p><ul><li><m> y \times -1 + x \times 7 = 4 </m></li><li><m> y \times -4 + x \times -1 = 7 </m></li></ul></statement><answer><ul><li><m> -4 </m></li><li><m> -\frac{7}{4} </m></li></ul></answer></exercise>
